    h2. Advocates, Innovators and Early Adopters
  
    * "Pete Muir":profile://petemuir - Co-founder of Arquillian. Created JBoss Test Harness, the precursor to Arquillian.
    * "Cheyenne Weaver":profile://cheyenneweaver - Brought Ike to life and gave Arquillian a "visual identity":http://design.jboss.org/arquillian
    * "Adrian Cole":profile://adriancole - Took Arquillian to the clouds (via "jclouds":http://jclouds.org); advocates it as a Java cloud power tool
    * "Paul Bakker":profile://pbakker - Created and maintains the Arquillian Forge plugin ("SEAMFORGE-146":issue://SEAMFORGE-146)
    * "Jesper Pedersen":profile://jesper.pedersen - Implemented the IronJacamar (embedded JCA) container adapter
    * "German Escobar":profile://germanescobar - Wrote about "testing a JMX CDI extension with Arquillian":http://community.jboss.org/wiki/TestingaJMXPortableExtensionforCDI
    * "Michael Schuetz":profile://michaelschuetz - Setup the "Arquillian sandbox":http://github.com/arquillian-sandbox repository, created quickstart projects, researched and wrote Seam 2 extension
    * "Adam Warski":profile://adamw - Worked out a solution for doing "efficient database-oriented testing":http://www.warski.org/blog/?p=325
    * "Markus Eisele":profile://myfear - Covered Arquillian in "Java Tech Journal March 2011":http://blog.eisele.net/2011/03/new-article-for-latest-jaxmag-java-ee-6.html
    * "Cosmin Martinconi":profile://CosminMartinconi (mentor: "Jakob Korherr":profile://jakobk) - "GSoC 2010 project":http://socghop.appspot.com/gsoc/student_project/show/google/gsoc2010/apache/t127230758773 to create an "automated webapp test suite for MyFaces":http://wiki.apache.org/myfaces/AutomatedWebappTest_Status based on the Arquillian SPI ("wrap-up":http://www.jakobk.com/2010/09/myfaces-webapptest-meets-apache-svn)
    * "John Ament":profile://meetoblivion - Wrote about "testing a property loader CDI extension with Arquillian":http://john-ament.blogspot.com/2010/03/writing-property-loader-in-java-ee-6.html
    * "Stuart Douglas":profile://swd847 - Converted Weld extensions tests to Arquillian, uses Arquillian to test fakereplace
    * "Jordan Ganoff":profile://jganoff - Wrote about "testing the Seam JMS module with Arquillian":http://community.jboss.org/wiki/Seam3JMSModuleTestingwithArquillian
    * "Lincoln Baxter III":profile://lincolnthree - Wrote about "CDI-powered unit testing with Arquillian":http://ocpsoft.com/seam/cdi-powered-unit-testing-using-arquillian/, uses Arquillian to test Seam Forge
